&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://spricoder.oss-cn-shanghai.aliyuncs.com/2019-Data-Structure/img/cpt10/54.png&#34;&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://quasdo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/54.png&#34; alt=&#34;img&#34; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
