&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://quasdo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/%E7%AC%AC4%E8%AE%B2%EF%BC%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF20200416_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_051.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;第4讲：网络层原理与技术20200416_页面_051&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://quasdo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/%E7%AC%AC4%E8%AE%B2%EF%BC%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF20200416_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_052.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;第4讲：网络层原理与技术20200416_页面_052&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;路由器需要做一个与运算，交换机不用&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://quasdo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/%E7%AC%AC4%E8%AE%B2%EF%BC%9A%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%B1%82%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86%E4%B8%8E%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF20200416_%E9%A1%B5%E9%9D%A2_053.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;第4讲：网络层原理与技术20200416_页面_053&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
